notes.content: In this Angular Http Post Example, we will show you how to make an HTTP Post Request to a back end server. We use the HttpClient module in Angular.

notes.title: Band of Brothers
notes.content: Band of Brothers is a 2001 American war drama miniseries based on historian Stephen E. Ambrose's 1992 non-fiction book of the same name. It was created by Steven Spielberg and Tom Hanks, who also served as executive producers, and who had collaborated on the 1998 World War II film Saving Private Ryan.
